This project is a standalone Maven benchmark measuring the wall-clock cost of
forking test JVMs versus running the same tests in-process, and the effect of the
C2 JIT compiler on that cost. It depends at build time on JUnit 5 (EPL-2.0) and
the Apache Maven Surefire Plugin (Apache-2.0), which are downloaded from Maven
Central and are not redistributed here.
